title: Women who made modern Britain
itunes:title: Women who made modern Britain
itunes:subtitle: Cathy Newman discusses trailblazing women who changed the course of modern British history.
description:
Journalist and news presenter Cathy Newman discusses her new book Bloody Brilliant Women, which tells the stories of trailblazing women who changed the course of modern British history.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
